99-0459 (La. 4/1/99)

BAYOU FLEET PARTNERSHIP v. Agnes. R. SAIA, Dominick M. Saia, Michelle A. Saia, and Lisa M. Saia, and Home Place Batture Leasing, Inc. No. 99-C-0459. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 1, 1999.

IN RE: Bayou Fleet Partnership;— Plaintiff(s); Applying for Writ of Certiora-ri and/or Review; to the Court of Appeal, Fifth Circuit, Number 98-CA-0306; Parish of Jefferson 24th Judicial District Court Div. “G” Number 489-381

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J. not on panel. LEMMON, TRAYLOR and KNOLL, JJ. would grant the writ.
